name: Playerlauncher
tagline: Repository dedicated to PlayerLauncher, a bukkit plugin.
body:
PlayerLauncher
=========

This GitHub page is dedicated to PlayerLauncher, a devBukkit Plugin. PlayerLauncher allows players to soar into the air with a command in Minecraft. PlayerLauncher v1.4.1 supports ALL versions of minecraft above 1.2.5. This includes 1.7.2!

PlayerLauncher is useful for several functions such as:
* A Donor perk
* Raiding, PvP, etc.
* Routine, dangerous tasks, such as fighting mobs or mining.
* And more!

The page has been designed to offer more comprehensive support towards using 
this bukkit plugin, found at http://dev.bukkit.org/bukkit-plugins/playerlauncher/

Visit the Wiki for any help with the plugin: https://github.com/AoHRuthless/PlayerLauncher/wiki

I hope you enjoy using my plugins; and if you have any issues, post them at https://github.com/AoHRuthless/PlayerLauncher/issues
